track_notes:
classification EE.
Summer clouds always cover these valleys early, so you need to start early in the morning.
I started in the night with headlamp belong the country road of Ciavanis till Pian Quarchietto. Some  problem to find the right way crossing towards Alpe Trail. Later, the day light helps me to reach lake Lee. From there you must search your way between rocks. Summit is ROCKY but you can use a lot of broken rocks.
track_title: class EE  Long trek NO path from Lake Lee Rocky summit
